md:
giải nghĩa từ "firsttime" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

1. First-time (adjective)
	* Meaning: happening or done for the first time
	* Vietnamese: lần đầu tiên
	* Example sentence: "This is my first-time visit to Paris."
	* Related words: first, time, visit

2. First-time (noun)
	* Meaning: an experience or event that is happening for the first time
	* Vietnamese: kinh nghiệm lần đầu tiên
	* Example sentence: "Skydiving was a thrilling first-time experience for me."
	* Related words: experience, event, thrilling

Note: The meaning of "first-time" can vary depending on the context in which it is used. In general, it refers to something that is happening or being done for the first time.
